{"tid":422515,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑不滿女友接其他男子來電 男侍應涉虐打女友兼揮舞菜刀","createTime":"2017-10-03T06:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T15:45:41.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5700748c1b32ae624bf3bf2de3fd02c43973f81e","tid":422515,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:20:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>疑不滿女友接其他男子來電 男侍應涉虐打女友兼揮舞菜刀</strong><br />\n<br />\n21歲男侍應與年長9歲的美容師成為情侶後，發現女友收到其他男子的來電，突然醋意大發，涉嫌緊捏女友頸項、將她推撞至牆及衣櫃，再檢查女友手機後質問：「點解你要背叛我？我做錯咗啲乜嘢？點解有咁多男仔搵你？」，再涉掟她的電話落地及揮舞菜刀，揚言殺死她。同晚男侍應再涉掌摑她、推她令她向後跌，頭顱撞碎窗玻璃、咬傷她手指，又要求她咬著拖鞋不要再出聲。<br />\n<br />\n案發於今年7月21日，男侍應王偉發被控襲擊傷人、刑事恐嚇、刑毀等共5罪，案件今於九龍城法院開審。"},{"pid":"442b3893ae1b5a7094a970a3f19990c1e9c97822","tid":422515,"uid":60764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:21:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7605ece7240b1c977f274ea37cb12802bae47849","tid":422515,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美容師？"},{"pid":"6178ad15b5ac00b125ea734ddafe53b77d87aa14","tid":422515,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:24:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美容師？</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勞</span></span>"},{"pid":"cc23612cabfdbd47946bae840540d7c42bc865a2","tid":422515,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:24:36.000Z","msg":"做得好呀"},{"pid":"927d09094d2d936c8ad6edff034deeb8a913cb79","tid":422515,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:27:59.000Z","msg":"真男人<br />\n打撚死班臭雞"},{"pid":"d068fbede0235be75087da2551ed5ebcb138780a","tid":422515,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma